{"id":48704,"date":"2025-03-13T13:41:51","date_gmt":"2025-03-13T08:11:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/?p=48704"},"modified":"2025-03-13T13:45:22","modified_gmt":"2025-03-13T08:15:22","slug":"software-internship-at-microsoft-ug-pg-students","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/internships\/software-internship-at-microsoft-ug-pg-students\/","title":{"rendered":"Software Internship at Microsoft [UG\/PG Students; 1 Year Exp in OOPs; Multiple Locations]: Apply Now!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>Applications are invited for the Software Internship at Microsoft. Check all the details below and apply before the link expires!<\/em><\/strong><\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>About Microsoft<\/strong><\/h2><p>Microsoft India (R&amp;D) Private Limited, a subsidiary of Microsoft Corporation, established the Microsoft India Development Center (MSIDC) in Hyderabad in 1998. Since then, it has grown to become one of the largest R&amp;D centres for Microsoft outside of its headquarters in Redmond.<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Internship Details<\/strong><\/h2><p>Software engineers (SWEs) at Microsoft collaborate with teams to develop innovative software solutions, focusing on customer needs and product quality. They provide technical guidance to Technical Program Managers and Product Managers, helping them consider user requirements and product specifications. SWEs are expected to learn and adopt new technologies, tools, methods, and processes to enhance their solutions.<\/p><p>Interns at Microsoft work on real-world projects, collaborating with global teams while having fun. They are encouraged to build community, explore their passions, and achieve their goals, all while contributing to cutting-edge technology.<\/p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"593\" src=\"https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-1024x593.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-48708\" style=\"width:635px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-1024x593.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-300x174.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-768x444.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-1536x889.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-2048x1185.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cse.noticebard.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2025\/03\/Software-Internship-at-Microsoft-Multiple-Locations-600x347.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Software Internship at Microsoft<\/figcaption><\/figure><p>Microsoft\u2019s mission is to empower every individual and organization to achieve more. With a growth mindset, a commitment to innovation, and a culture rooted in respect, integrity, and accountability, Microsoft fosters an inclusive environment where employees thrive.<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Responsibilities<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Applies engineering principles to solve complex problems through sound and creative engineering.<\/li>\n\n<li>Quickly learns new engineering methods and incorporates them into work processes.<\/li>\n\n<li>Seeks feedback and applies internal or industry best practices to improve technical solutions.<\/li>\n\n<li>Demonstrates time management skills and completing software projects in a cooperative team environment.<\/li><\/ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Qualifications<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Pursuing a bachelor&#8217;s or master&#8217;s degree in engineering, computer science or related field.<\/li>\n\n<li>Must have at least one additional quarter\/semester of school remaining following the completion of the internship.<\/li>\n\n<li>One year of programming experience in an object-oriented language.<\/li><\/ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>How to Apply?<\/strong><\/h2><p>Interested and eligible candidates can directly <a href=\"https:\/\/jobs.careers.microsoft.com\/global\/en\/job\/1743242\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/jobs.careers.microsoft.com\/global\/en\/job\/1743242\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">apply through this link<\/a>.<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Location<\/strong><\/h2><p>Multiple Locations, India.<\/p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/jobs.careers.microsoft.com\/global\/en\/job\/1743242\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/jobs.careers.microsoft.com\/global\/en\/job\/1743242\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to view the Software Internship at Microsoft.<\/a><\/strong><\/h3><p><em><a href=\"https:\/\/uhf.microsoft.com\/images\/microsoft\/RE1Mu3b.png\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/uhf.microsoft.com\/images\/microsoft\/RE1Mu3b.png\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Image Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Applications are invited for the Software Internship at Microsoft. Check all the details below and apply before the link expires! About Microsoft Microsoft India (R&amp;D) Private Limited, a subsidiary of Microsoft Corporation, established the Microsoft India Development Center (MSIDC) in Hyderabad in 1998. Since then, it has grown to become one of the largest R&amp;D [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13860,"featured_media":48706,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"clo